data.description: Welcome home to 24350 Russell Avenue. Clean and well maintained home. The aluminum siding was freshed with a coat of paint in the not too distant past. The ranch style home features 3 bedrooms and 1-1/2 baths. The baths and kitchen were both remodeled several years ago. Kitchen features Maple Kraftmaid cabinets. The home has beautiful hardwood floors throughout the first floor. The basement rec room is 40 feet long - large enough for any gathering. Other past updates included a roof in 2001, and furnace and central air in 2002. Home also has a 2 car detached garage and enough room behind the garage to put in your own vegetable and/or herb garden. Make your appointment to see it today.  Point of sale is ordered. Buyer will need to assume. Will post as soon as I have available.
